# Technology Requirements

This rule specifies the technology versions and requirements for the AI Primitives platform.

## Applies to
**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json}

## Rule
### Core Technologies
- TypeScript: ^5.7.3
- Node.js: ^20 ||^22
- Package Manager: pnpm ^9 || ^10

### Frontend
- Next.js: ^15.2.4
- React: ^19.0.0
- React DOM: ^19.0.0
- Vercel for deployment and preview environments

### Backend
- Payload CMS: ^3.28.1
- MongoDB (via @payloadcms/db-mongodb): latest
- Cloudflare Workers (for APIs)
- Hono: ^4.7.4
- Zod: ^3.24.1
- Composio for underlying infrastructure

### Development Tools
- ESLint: ^9.16.0
- Prettier: ^3.5.3
- TypeScript: ^5.7.3
- Wrangler: ^4.2.0
- Changesets for version management
